\begin{aligned}
\bar{M}_n &= \sum x_i M_i = x_1 M_1 + x_2 M_2 \\
&= 0.4 \cdot 50,000 + 0.6 \cdot 80,000 \\
&= 20,000 + 48,000 = 68,000 \text{ g/mol} \\
