&= 0.3 \cdot 50,000 + 0.7 \cdot 80,000 \\
&= 15,000 + 56,000 = 71,000 \text{ g/mol} \\
\text{Thus, } \bar{M}_w = 71,000 \text{ g/mol} \ \checkmark
\end{aligned}

